      "source": "memory",
      "snippet": "1. Через Playwright достаём m78 URL (аудио-дорожка отдельно от инстаграма) 2. ffmpeg: combine video (q70/VP9) + audio (m78/AAC) → H.264 + AAC @ 1080×1920 **Команда:** ```bash ffmpeg -i reel_hd.mp4 -i reel_audio.mp4 \\ -c:v libx264 -profile:v main -preset fast -crf 23 \\ -vf \"scale=1080:1920:force_original_aspect_ratio=decrease,pad=1080:1920:(ow-iw)/2:(oh-ih)/2,setsar=1,fps=30\" \\ -c:a aac -b:a 128k -shortest \\ -pix_fmt yuv420p -movflags +faststart \\ reel_tiktok_ready.mp4 ```",
